title: Ep 2719 - Jethalal Plans To Expose Sevaklal
shortDesc: Jethalal and all his friends sit together for a meeting to plan how to uncover the truth of Sevaklal. after so many discussions finally, Popatlal discovers an idea to execute to catch Sevaklal. To know more, stay tuned!

title: Ep 2720 - Execution Of The Plan
shortDesc: Jethalal and his whole group gets on his way to the location of delivery and prosecutes with his plan. And he makes them believe that he is with them to help them in distributing the mobiles.

title: Ep 2721 - Jethalal In Trouble
shortDesc: As we know Sevaklal started distributing the mobiles in the slums and even Jethalal and Popatlal helped them in doing the same. And in the later stage, when Sevaklal asked for more 5000 mobiles Jethalal tries escaping away from the place.

title: Ep 2722 - Mission Successful
shortDesc: Finally and the whole team gets success in their mission. They successfully expose the real face of Sevaklal who was just fooling the people for mobiles in exchange of votes. But knowing the reality, even they refused to support Sevaklal.

title: Ep 2723 - Sevaklals Truth
shortDesc: After the handlers of Sevaklal get apprehended, they deny all the allegations against Sevaklal and pin the whole act on Jethalal. Sodhi tells them that they have the recording, Bhide breaks it to him that the recordings got destroyed.

title: Ep 2724 - Jethalals Celebration
shortDesc: Jethalal is celebrating and giving out sweets to people in the society, two pieces at a time: one for his 'Jeet' and the other for the sale of his mobile phone. Stay tuned to find out what happens next.

title: Ep 2725 - Champaklal Returns
shortDesc: Champaklal returns from his trip at an odd time. Jethalal and Tappu are worried because no one rings the doorbell at 4:00 AM but when they get to know that its Champaklal, both of them are delighted.

title: Ep 2726 - Hunger Pangs
shortDesc: Atmaram and Madhavi are busy making pickles when they get a visit from Jethalal. Seeing them so busy, especially Madhavi he feels guilty to put more work on them as he actually wanted some food but he changes his request.

title: Ep 2727 - The Visiting Couple
shortDesc: Jethalal is on his way to the shop with Taarak Mehta when he gets a call saying there is a couple at the shop who are waiting to meet him. After reaching the shop, he becomes furious thinking they are gone.

title: Ep 2728 - The Mystery Caller
shortDesc: Jethalal calls his friend, suspecting him of playing a prank on him with the couple from the previous episode but his friend denied this. Now Jethalal is even more confused and continues to call his contacts one after the other hoping to find out th

title: Ep 2729 - Dinner For Visitors
shortDesc: Jethalal goes for grocery shopping. he buys two varieties of everything on his shopping list because the handwriting is unclear to him. otherwise, he is enjoying this experience of visiting the vegetable market after a long time.

title: Ep 2730 - Unknown Guests
shortDesc: "Jethalal and Babita are busy making dinner but Jethalal is more focused on Babita than on cooking. As they finish cooking and wait around awkwardly for the guest to arrive, they are surprised to see the new unknown visitors.

title: Ep 2731 - Before They Arrive
shortDesc: The guys are still waiting for the real guests to arrive when they get a visit from Taarak and Anjali who wanted to also meet their guest. Anjali is angry at Jethalal for not telling her that guest would be arriving .

title: Ep 2732 - Faces Revealed
shortDesc: The mysterious guests finally take off their mask and reveal themselves and Jethalal gets too excited seeing their faces. Chandu Bhai with his wife has returned from America!

title: Ep 2733 - Old Friends
shortDesc: After the reveal of the special guest is done, they have a joyous time and then meet the rest of the Gokuldhaam society and as usual Popatlal never misses to pitch himself as a desperate bachelor. Stay tuned for more fun.
